OL,6,F"Once you've got past the diagnosis,
OL,7,Fwhich for me was over two years ago,
OL,8,Fnow the first part of that is pretty
OL,9,Fgrim and then you start treatment,"
OL,10,FHoy added.
OL,12,F"Then, if you're lucky like me, you
OL,13,Frespond to the treatment and then you
OL,14,Fenter a period of kind of stability.
